{"type":"message","id":"2c73d23c","parentId":"e955dc59","timestamp":"2026-03-25T10:10:29.932Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-25 18:10:05 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-embodied_ai] DM | ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57 [msg:om_x100b530f097158a0c29a4815b7bf70c, post, 1 attachment(s)]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b530f097158a0c29a4815b7bf70c\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-25 18:10 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\"\n}\n```\n\n[Image]\nUser text:\n[Feishu ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57 Wed 2026-03-25 18:10 GMT+8] ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57: /home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/media/inbound/0eced794-9987-4541-b9a2-9664740fee0b.jpg\n页面上画的这个图是什么意思？\nDescription:\nThis diagram depicts a robot control architecture. A frozen Eagle-2 VLM processes visual and text inputs. These outputs, combined with encoded robot states and noised actions, pass through $N$ Diffusion-Transformer (DiT) blocks. Following $K$ denoising iterations, an Action Decoder generates a sequence of motor actions ($a_t$ to $a_{t+H-1}$) for a humanoid robot. Green modules are embodiment-specific, while blue-marked ones are pre-trained and frozen."}],"timestamp":1774433429929}}
