{"type":"message","id":"8994e843","parentId":"9bb05093","timestamp":"2026-03-25T10:10:50.623Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发送了一张图片，询问图中的架构是什么意思。根据系统提供的图片描述，这是一个机器人控制架构图，包含：\n1. Eagle-2 VLM（视觉语言模型）- 处理视觉和文本输入\n2. 编码的机器人状态和加噪声的动作\n3. N个Diffusion-Transformer (DiT) blocks\n4. K次去噪迭代\n5. Action Decoder生成动作序列\n6. 绿色模块是embodiment-specific，蓝色是预训练且冻结的\n\n这看起来是一个基于扩散模型的机器人控制策略，结合了视觉语言模型。让我读取这张图片来更准确地解读。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9a507854a27647a6911a0231","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/media/inbound/0eced794-9987-4541-b9a2-9664740fee0b.jpg"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":11103,"output":315,"cacheRead":2752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14170,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774433440502,"responseId":"20260325181040720408b254ca4cbd"}}
