{"type":"message","id":"68f8065d","parentId":"504a88b4","timestamp":"2026-03-25T10:13:22.178Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-25 18:13:14 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-embodied_ai] DM | ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57 [msg:om_x100b530f1d6ddca0c4f20027bf79a92]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b530f1d6ddca0c4f20027bf79a92\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-25 18:13 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\"\n}\n```\n\n这个模型是lerobot研发的？它不是具身智能模型框架吗？"}],"timestamp":1774433602174}}
{"type":"message","id":"79573585","parentId":"68f8065d","timestamp":"2026-03-25T10:13:32.906Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User asks if the model is developed by lerobot and if it's not a embodied AI framework. Need answer.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]  \n是的，这张图里展示的 **Diffusion‑Transformer + VLM** 控制结构正是 **LeRobot**（🤗 LeRobot）团队研发的核心模型之一。LeRobot 本身是 **具身智能（Embodied AI）框架**，它把视觉‑语言理解、机器人状态编码和扩散动作生成统一在一个端到端的网络里。\n\n- **模型来源**：LeRobot 在源码 `lerobot/models/` 下提供了多个实现（如 `DiffusionPolicy`, `VLMPolicy`），图中的架构对应的是 **VLM‑augmented Diffusion Policy**——把 **Eagle‑2 VLM**（冻结的大模型）与 **Diffusion‑Transformer (DiT)** 结合，用来预测连续的机器人动作序列。  \n- **框架定位**：LeRobot 旨在 **统一训练与评估具身智能任务**（行为克隆、强化学习、视觉‑语言‑动作等），所以它既是 **模型库**（提供这些 SoTA 模型的实现），也是 **整体实验框架**（数据接口、训练脚本、评估基准）。\n\n简言之，图里的模型正是 LeRobot 框架里的一种 **具体模型实现**，而 LeRobot 整体则是一个 **具身智能、机器人学习的完整框架**。如果想进一步跑实验或微调，只需要在 LeRobot 环境中准备好数据集并调用对应的 `lerobot train` / `lerobot evaluate` 即可。😁"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":14777,"output":396,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15173,"cost":{"input":-14777,"output":-396,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-15173}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774433602178,"responseId":"gen-1774433607-b8egupoq0FYoaEHq9WxT"}}
