{"type":"message","id":"d4f7f702","parentId":"169a9d72","timestamp":"2026-03-25T10:16:04.549Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Need to give model name. Based on diagram likely \"Eagle-2 VLM + Diffusion Transformer policy\". Could be called \"Eagle-2 Diffusion Policy\" or \"VLM‑augmented Diffusion Policy\". Provide name.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]  \n这套架构在 **LeRobot** 中通常被称为 **“Eagle‑2 VLM + Diffusion‑Transformer Policy”**（也叫 **VLM‑augmented Diffusion Policy**）。它把 **Eagle‑2 视觉语言模型** 与 **Diffusion‑Transformer（DiT）** 结合，用来一次性生成机器人未来 H 步的动作序列。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":15684,"output":202,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15886,"cost":{"input":-15684,"output":-202,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-15886}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774433752301,"responseId":"gen-1774433757-Fm5TAQtuSAUrHeowlFl7"}}
