{"type":"message","id":"9a8e4771","parentId":"80a0bf1b","timestamp":"2026-03-25T10:16:57.038Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User asks \"是VLA骂醒？\" likely means \"Is it VLA?\" maybe typo. Answer that it's VLA (Vision-Language-Action) model.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]  \n是的，图中展示的模型属于 **VLA（Vision‑Language‑Action）** 系列——即把视觉、语言指令和动作生成统一在同一个网络里。它通过 Eagle‑2 VLM 读取图像和文字，再用 Diffusion‑Transformer 生成连续的机器人动作序列。这样就实现了 **“看图+听指令 → 做动作”** 的端到端 VLA 能力。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":16355,"output":177,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16532,"cost":{"input":-16355,"output":-177,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-16532}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774433808100,"responseId":"gen-1774433813-VM2mD0mOljJwv6lglRzh"}}
