{"type":"message","id":"b8c56ee0","parentId":"0095c8c4","timestamp":"2026-03-25T10:17:39.235Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]  \n下面是与 **Eagle‑2 VLM + Diffusion‑Transformer（VLA）** 相关的论文链接，你可以直接打开阅读：\n\n- **GR00T N1: An Open Foundation Model for Generalist Humanoid Robots**  \n  https://arxiv.org/abs/2503.14734v2  \n\n这篇论文详细介绍了 **Vision‑Language‑Action (VLA)** 双系统架构、Eagle‑2 VLM 以及 Diffusion‑Transformer（DiT）在机器人动作生成中的作用。祝你阅读顺利！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":19210,"output":133,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19343,"cost":{"input":-19210,"output":-133,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-19343}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774433856800,"responseId":"gen-1774433856-1LcMpoAAYVqVfcg8NFCX"}}
