{"type":"message","id":"25e7a42d","parentId":"779e731c","timestamp":"2026-03-25T10:18:49.492Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Need to answer: who created GR00T N1. From paper authors list includes many NVIDIA authors. So it's NVIDIA team. Provide answer.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]  \n**GR00T N1** 是 **NVIDIA** 研发的开源基础模型，论文的作者全部是 NVIDIA 的研究团队成员（包括 Johan Bjorck、Fernando Castañeda、Nikita Cherniadev、Xingye Da 等多人）。因此，这个模型可以算作 NVIDIA 的作品。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":19925,"output":149,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20074,"cost":{"input":-19925,"output":-149,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-20074}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774433920816,"responseId":"gen-1774433926-IgAv4Qa5adytgVXBl3ck"}}
